The tables should be organised in a way such that<br><ul><li>No data is&nbsp;<b>unnecessarily duplicated</b>.</li><li>Data is&nbsp;<b>consistent</b>&nbsp;throughout the database.</li><li>The struture of each table should be flexible to allow&nbsp;<b>as many or as few </b>items.</li><li>The structure should enable a user to&nbsp;<b>make all kinds of complex queries</b>&nbsp;relating data from different tables.</li></ul>